com.paydiant.android.ui.service.receipt

Interface IReceiptRetrievalWithSplitTenderInfoListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IReceiptRetrievalListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ReceiptRetrievalListenerAdapter

    public interface IReceiptRetrievalWithSplitTenderInfoListener
extends IReceiptRetrievalListener
    This listener interface provides support for retrieval of receipts with split tender information. In order to register for callback events, an instance of this would needed to be set through the IReceiptRetrievalService.setReceiptRetrievalListener(IReceiptRetrievalListener) method. This must be set before invoking any of the service operations.

    Note: App developers are encouraged to use the ListenerAdapter implementations whenever possible as the Listener interfaces might get updated with new functionality/methods from one SDK release to the other. Therefore using a ListenerAdapter will make sure that there wont be any compilation issues due to unimplemented methods during a SDK upgrade.

    Since:
    3.5.0.1
    Author:
    Paydiant Inc.
    See Also:
    ReceiptRetrievalListenerAdapter
